Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,地球脉动 III
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}字幕翻译：村儿南
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,尼泊尔 萨乌拉哈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sauraha, Nepal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.40,0:01:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这头犀牛没有迷路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This rhino is not lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它正向着食物进发\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is on his way to find food.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,为此 它必须穿越一个陌生而新奇的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To get it, he must travel through a new and alien world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.20,0:01:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这头犀牛一生中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This rhino in his lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,见证了太多前所未有的变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has seen more changes than any of his previous generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在世界各地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Across the globe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,各种动物都不得不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}animals of all kinds are now contending
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,与一种新的优势物种竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with one newly dominant species...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,和很多野生动物一样 犀牛不得不学会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like so many wild creatures, he's had to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如何在人类世界中生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how to live in the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}第7集\N人类世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.52,0:02:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有些动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some animals
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,已经改变了自己的习性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have changed their behaviour
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以便在人类身边获得更多的好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make the most out of living amongst us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.56,0:02:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些长尾猕猴生活在巴厘岛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These long-tailed macaques live in Bali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它们对人类游客带来的新东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have developed new interests
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}brought by human visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,每天早上 长尾猕猴群都会前往\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every morning, the troop heads for a building
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,领地中央的一座建筑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the centre of their territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.24,0:03:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,乌鲁瓦图寺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uluwatu Temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这里每天都有熙熙攘攘的游客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tourists come here every day - in crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,因此只要熟门熟路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So the temple grounds are full of opportunities...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,寺院里到处都是机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...if you know where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,眼花缭乱的帽子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is a constant supply of hats...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,以及墨镜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.56,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只要出其不意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you've mastered the element of surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.96,0:04:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,便能手到擒来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...it's easy to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但这些东西不是用来吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this harvest is not for eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而是用来做交易的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's for bargaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,交易愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems like a fair trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而对于一些见多识广的猕猴来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there are greater rewards to be had
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,它们瞄准了更大的目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for those who know how to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这只年迈的雄猕猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this old male appears to be doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎游刃有余\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这些久经世故的猕猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He and the other elders in this troop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,经验丰富 见多识广\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}have both experience and knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在寺院里生活了十多年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've been working the temple for over ten years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,专抢那些人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now concentrate on the big stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:06:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,离不得的重要物品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...things that human beings just can't do without.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,鞋子丢了还怎么走回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No-one wants to walk home with just one shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这群年长猕猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these old boys can't wait
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也想体验一把新科技\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to get their hands on the latest tech.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,它们摸准了人类的心理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've worked out that we simply can't survive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,手机万万丢不得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without our phones...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,钱包也同样如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...or our wallets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,久经世故的雄猕猴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The older males understand
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,掌握了一种小猕猴还没学会的技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}something the youngsters have yet to learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.72,0:07:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,交易的艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the art of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,才一根香蕉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A banana?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一块巧克力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A bar of chocolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这还差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的技术在于谈判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The real skill is in the negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,猕猴用人类的方式对付人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The macaques are playing us at our own game.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They demand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,予取予求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...whatever they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的足迹已经遍布世界每一个角落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humanity has spread to every corner of the globe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,扮演自然的角色 改变世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have become a force of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人类改造了80%的地表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have altered 80% of the land's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,足有80亿人口生活在地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eight billion people now live on this planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正以惊人的速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and we are changing the world around us
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,改变周遭世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at such speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,如此快速变化的世界 给动物带来了严峻挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that, for animals, the challenge is to keep up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,纽约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蚂蚁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,观点指出 这种蚂蚁随着第一批欧洲移民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This particular species is thought to have arrived here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,登上了这片大陆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the first European settlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,被称为辅道蚁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are now known as pavement ants
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它们几乎只存在于人类城镇中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because they live almost exclusively in our towns and cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,辅道蚁种群的旺盛 得益于垃圾食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And they're thriving because of junk food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 百老汇大道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here on Broadway Avenue,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都是辅道蚁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there's a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是辅道蚁梦寐以求的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is what every pavement ant desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,为了得到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And to get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,辅道蚁利用了城市中数千里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the ants use the city's thousands of miles
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,地下隧道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of underground tunnels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这只侦查蚁正接近目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This scout is closing in on its target.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走在同一条道路上的人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the animals with which they share the pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,重量是辅道蚁的4000万倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are 40 million times their weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以最好还是缩在裂缝中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...so it's best to stay in the cracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,中了头奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.88,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一座肉山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A meat mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅一只辅道蚁 搬不走这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is too big a job for just one ant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如同每只工蚁一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This worker is female,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这只工蚁是雌性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as they are in all ant colonies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它通过信息素标记路径\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she leaves a trail of pheromones to mark a path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,返回巢穴的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She communicates with every sister she meets
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它把消息告诉给了每一个工蚁姐妹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as she returns to the nest,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.96,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个消息很快便传开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and news on the street spreads fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这种超加工肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This ultra-processed meat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,和辅道蚁原本的食性完全不同\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is very different from their original food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,辅道蚁成功的关键 在于消化系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But their digestive system is the key to their success.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.48,0:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的消化系统能适应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's able to keep up with the way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人类不断变化的饮食习惯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}humans constantly change their diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 辅道蚁的绝大多数食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nowadays, the vast majority of what they eat
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都来自于人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}comes from human food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,仅在百老汇大道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On Broadway alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,辅道蚁每年吃掉的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}pavement ants eat the equivalent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,足足相当于6万根热狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of a staggering 60,000 hot dogs every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一根热狗提供的卡路里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The calories in a single hot dog
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,可以满足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}could fuel the growth
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,整个辅道蚁群一个月的需要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the entire ant colony for a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只要它们能把食物运回巢穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...if only they can get it back to the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然而这种慢功夫相当危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this slow work makes them vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,辅道蚁不是唯一喜欢快餐的生物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They aren't the only ones partial to fast food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因此它们必须尽快把战利品运回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a race to get their prize home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会有牺牲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There may be losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但整个蚁群将得以壮大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but the colony as a whole will now thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上在纽约 辅道蚁的生存策略非常成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In fact, pavement ants are so successful here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,种群数量达到了纽约市民的一千倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that they outnumber human New Yorkers 1,000 to 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,然而在人类世界中 声名狼藉的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But success in the human world can be harder to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,往往很难取得成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if your reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在印度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here in India,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这条眼镜蛇正直奔一个村庄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this cobra is heading directly for a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它闻到了猎物的气息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has detected the scent of prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,近两米长的眼镜蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nearly two metres long,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一口咬下去释放的毒液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it has enough venom in a single bite
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,足以杀死十个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to kill ten people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在印度 每年近6万人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Snake bites are responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因被蛇咬伤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for nearly 60,000 deaths a year
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in India alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.40,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜蛇无声无息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They travel so silently
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.96,0:15:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很难察觉到它们的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that their presence is often undetected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当眼镜蛇捕猎时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when they are hunting...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它们无处不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...there is no place they won't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一只蟾蜍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A toad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜蛇分叉的舌头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each tip of its forked tongue
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能够收集猎物的化学信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}collects chemical signals from the prey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助确定猎物方位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and helps to reveal its position.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但到了近距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But up close...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,眼镜蛇依靠视觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the snake relies on movement
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来精确定位猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to precisely locate its prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蟾蜍必须把握好逃跑的时机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The toad must pick its moment to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蟾蜍每次跳跃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every time it touches the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,都会在地上留下气味\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the toad leaves behind a scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,蟾蜍藏了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It can hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.36,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但眼镜蛇能循着气味痕迹找到它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but the trail will lead the snake to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些眼镜蛇不仅只在这里捕猎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These cobras don't just hunt here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,还在这里生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,此处的的印度教村民尊敬它们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have found a home where the Hindu villagers revere them
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,认为眼镜蛇是神灵的化身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and consider them to be demigods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊讶的是 科学家认为 人类对眼镜蛇的容让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remarkably, scientists believe that this tolerance
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,导致了眼镜蛇习性的转变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has led to a change in the snakes' behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们移动得更慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They move more slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,并且应激下的攻击行为也有所减少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and are less likely to strike if disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,作为地球上最令人恐惧的动物之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of the most feared animals on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,却找到了一处得到人类接纳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has found a place where they are accepted
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能与人类和平共处的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and can coexist with human beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 对于许多生活在人类世界的动物来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for many animals living in the human world,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,保持低调更为明智\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it pays to keep a low profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在澳大利亚墨尔本\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here in Melbourne, Australia,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一种动物完美掌握了伪装的艺术\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one creature has perfected the art of camouflage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,一只蛙嘴夜鹰雏鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A frogmouth chick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,白天 雏鹰的父亲帮助它隐藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Its father helps to hide it during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.76,0:19:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,蛙嘴夜鹰是夜行性鸟类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are nocturnal birds,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,夜晚降临时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and as day turns to night,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,蛙嘴夜鹰父母飞出阴影\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}its parents come out of the shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,享受城市生活的好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to reap the rewards of urban living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,城市灯光营造了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The city lights create
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,绝佳的捕猎条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}excellent conditions for hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.88,0:20:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,都市的每个夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every night in the city
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都仿佛圆月高挂般明亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is as bright as when there is a full moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因此城里的蛙嘴夜鹰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So city frogmouths often...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,往往能大饱口福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...have their mouths full.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这只雏鹰长得很快 它今天有些坐不住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's growing fast, and today he just won't sit still.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它的行踪暴露了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now he has revealed his presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蛙口夜鹰的第一要务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first rule of frogmouth behaviour is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,便是在白天不要动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't move in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:21:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是蛙口夜鹰一生中唯一一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But this is the one time in a frogmouth's life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,克制不住飞翔的冲动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when the urge to fly simply cannot be suppressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.36,0:21:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,然而它还没有做好离家的准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's not ready to leave home just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,夜幕降临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come night-time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.72,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鹰又饿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...he's hungry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它精神抖擞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is wide awake...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想要继续它的冒险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and wants to take off where he left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但它引来了不必要的注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's getting unwanted attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而这次父母无法在身边保护它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this time his parent is not nearby to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,人类宠物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humans bring pets,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在澳大利亚 每天有一百万只鸟死于猫爪下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and cats in Australia kill a million birds a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,雏鹰首次真正的飞行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His first proper flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但除非它能找到一个安全的落脚处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But unless he can find a safe place to roost,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.32,0:23:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,否则它依然处于危险之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he is still in peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,如果雏鹰想要在城市里生存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if he is to survive in the city, like the adults,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它必须学会如何与环境融为一体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he'll have to learn how to blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.84,0:23:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有些动物则非常胆大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some animals are so bold
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.24,0:23:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它们根本不怕被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that they don't even try to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,在人类世界中 大型捕食动物十分罕见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To see a large predator in the built-up world is a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.76,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而在北美太浩湖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here in Lake Tahoe, in North America,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这些体型庞大的黑熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}these black bears are particularly big...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.64,0:24:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,正朝着城镇中心走去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and they're heading right to the centre of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,冬天即将来临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Winter is approaching,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.16,0:24:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这些黑熊需要赶在下雪前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and these bears need to put on as much weight as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,尽可能增重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before the snow arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而这是一个大快朵颐的好地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a great place to gorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.04,0:24:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里现在是黑熊的天下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's now bear country.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.08,0:24:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,既然过个马路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why struggle for a meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就能吃到外卖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...when you can cross the street...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,又何必费力捕猎呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...for a takeaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.92,0:24:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的食物多到吃不完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's so much food here
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:25:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,以至于有些黑熊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that some of the bears are 50% heavier
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.48,0:25:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,比野外的同胞重50%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than their country cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.00,0:25:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但只是外卖还不够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But why stop here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.72,0:25:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有些黑熊更愿意堂食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some bears just want to dine in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,只有少数幸运的黑熊 能够从人类世界得到一顿简餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A lucky few are able to get an easy meal from the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 当人类进入自然界寻找食物时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But when WE venture to the natural world in search of food...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.92,0:25:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,索取的规模之大 无可比拟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the harvest is on a different scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.08,0:25:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,短短40年里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In just four decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.12,0:25:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,捕鱼活动使鱼类数量减半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fishing reduced fish populations by half...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.44,0:25:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并且给以此为食的海洋捕食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and created great problems for the ocean predators
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.96,0:25:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,带来了巨大的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that once had such food to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.44,0:26:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在温哥华岛海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Off the coast of Vancouver Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,座头鲸生活在一片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}humpback whales inhabit waters
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.80,0:26:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,鲱鱼被过度捕捞的海域\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where herring have been overfished.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.64,0:26:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,座头鲸有着丰富的创造力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humpbacks, however, are renowned for their ingenuity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.64,0:26:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,12年前 一头名为康格的雄鲸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}12 years ago, an adult male called Conger
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.04,0:26:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,发明了一种全新的捕食方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}adopted a totally new way of feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.88,0:26:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当水中的鱼类丰度过低\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When the density of fish in the water is low,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.08,0:26:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,鸟类潜入水下捕鱼时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and birds are diving to catch them...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.76,0:26:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,座头鲸大张嘴巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...the humpback opens its mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.76,0:26:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,使得鱼类误以为这里能够躲避捕食者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and creates a space that the fish mistake for shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.00,0:26:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼类纷纷涌入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fish swim in...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.88,0:27:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,陷阱随之合上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and the trap is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.16,0:27:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,康格是第一头被发现有如此行为的座头鲸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Conger was the first humpback whale to be seen doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.72,0:27:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如今这片海域 有30头座头鲸使用这种捕食技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now 30 whales in the area use this same technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.40,0:27:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,此处的座头鲸数量正在增长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The population of humpbacks here is growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.60,0:27:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会认为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you might think that this would
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.16,0:27:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这会使鱼类数量愈发减少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}reduce fish stocks even more,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,然而令人惊讶的事情正在发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but something surprising is thought to be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.32,0:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这些微小的浮游植物是食物链的基础\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These tiny phytoplankton are the basis of the food chain
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.52,0:27:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的生长依赖于一种重要的营养成分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and need a vital ingredient to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.48,0:27:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,铁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Iron.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.32,0:28:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,鲸鱼的粪便富含铁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whale faeces are rich in iron...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.84,0:28:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大型鲸鱼排出大量粪便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and great whales produce it in enormous quantities...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.96,0:28:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,浮游植物因此得以繁荣生长 为鲱鱼提供食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...so the phytoplankton flourishes, and herring feed on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.32,0:28:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上 鲸鱼粪便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whale faeces, in fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.68,0:28:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,正在帮助整个生态系统复苏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are helping to restore the whole ecosystem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.48,0:28:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,鲱鱼吸引海鸟前来捕食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The herring attract seabirds,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.16,0:28:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,潜入水下的海鸟从鱼群下方袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}diving birds attack them from beneath,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.72,0:28:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,海鸥和海雀则从上方俯冲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and gulls and shearwaters dive on them from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至白头海雕也能从盛宴中分一杯羹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even bald eagles benefit from this rich feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.00,0:29:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊讶的是 尽管康格等座头鲸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Astonishingly, even though Conger and all the other whales
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.60,0:29:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对鱼类大快朵颐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are feasting on fish,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.24,0:29:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但它们作为多样性生态系统不可或缺的一环\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their role in fertilising the ocean is so influential
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.96,0:29:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上使得这片海域的鲱鱼数量不降反增\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that herring numbers here are actually predicted to increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.24,0:29:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这在恢复环境方面所发挥的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the role they play in rejuvenating the environment...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.36,0:29:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,正对人类世界产生深远的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...is having an even greater impact on the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.36,0:30:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,繁荣生长的浮游植物如同树木一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The flourishing plankton also collects carbon
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.40,0:30:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,吸收大量的二氧化碳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the atmosphere, just as trees do...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.28,0:30:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,每头大型鲸鱼对于碳循环的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...so much so that each great whale
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.04,0:30:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,相当于一片三万棵树的森林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has the same impact as a forest of 30,000 trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.88,0:30:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大型鲸鱼曾一度遭到捕杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our great whales were once hunted...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.80,0:30:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,如果鲸鱼数量能恢复到此前的数量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and if they return to their pre-whaling numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.04,0:30:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,将相当于种植\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's estimated that this would be equivalent to planting
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.76,0:30:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,超过三百亿颗树\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}over 30 billion trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.12,0:31:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 鲸鱼被认为有益于人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whales are now being recognised as benefiting humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.12,0:31:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于大多数大型动物来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for most large animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.92,0:31:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,与人类的竞争造成了冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}competition with humans brings conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.20,0:31:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这只重达六吨雄性非洲象正值壮年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This six-tonne African bull elephant is in his prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.40,0:31:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为了在争夺雌性的战斗中占据优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To stand the best chance of winning fights for females,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.80,0:31:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它需要变得更壮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he needs to be big.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.64,0:31:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,它能闻到富含营养的食物就在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can smell highly nutritious food is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.72,0:31:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但为此它将不得不进入人类的领地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But crossing the boundary to reach it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.84,0:31:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这会是一趟危险的旅程\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is a dangerous journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.20,0:32:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,雄象必须等到夜幕降临\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He must wait for the cover of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.28,0:32:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些肯尼亚的农民正在为夜晚做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These Kenyan farmers are preparing for the night ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,两个月来 他们不得不每个夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have had to guard their crops every night
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.44,0:32:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都守在庄稼旁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the last two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.84,0:32:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,离收割庄稼只有两天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With only two days until harvest,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.52,0:32:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是关键时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is a critical time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.00,0:32:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一夜之间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a single night,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.48,0:32:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,一只雄象就可以摧毁十个农民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a bull elephant can destroy the entire crops
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.80,0:32:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一整季的收成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}produced by ten farmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.36,0:33:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,雄象决定冒这个险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's taking a huge risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.76,0:33:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雄象是人类的两倍高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's twice the height of a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.64,0:33:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,并且不会轻易退缩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and he won't back down easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.88,0:33:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这种人类与野生动物间的冲突 每个晚上都在发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This human-wildlife conflict happens night after night.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.40,0:34:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,每年 仅在肯尼亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And each year, it takes the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.28,0:34:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,就有多达200只大象和20个人因此丧生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of up to 200 elephants and 20 people in Kenya alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.56,0:34:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这场对峙可能会是致命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This standoff is potentially lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.64,0:34:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,农民不得不寻求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The farmers have had to call for help
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.04,0:34:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,一支经验丰富的护林队伍的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from a team of highly experienced rangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.24,0:34:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管他们全副武装\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although they're armed,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.60,0:34:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的任务是在不伤害大象的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}their task is to drive the elephant out of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.04,0:34:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,将其赶出田地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without harming it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.72,0:34:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 雄象打定了主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the bull is determined...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.04,0:34:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,拒不退让\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...to hold ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.76,0:35:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,护林员不得不一步一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rangers will have to get closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.04,0:35:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,向大象靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...on foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.12,0:35:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,护林员不得不使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rangers have to resort...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.20,0:35:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,鞭炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...to firecrackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.52,0:35:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,雄象被赶出了这片田地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bull is driven from this field...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.96,0:35:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,退回到灌木丛深处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and retreats deep into the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.40,0:36:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fortunately for this bull,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.04,0:36:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这场冲突得到了和平解决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the battle has been resolved peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.52,0:36:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的努力正在减少大象丧生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And efforts like these are seeing fewer elephants killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.60,0:36:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并且肯尼亚的大象数量 也再次开始增长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and their population in Kenya is starting to rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 人类活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But conflict with wildlife
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.76,0:36:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,大幅改变地球气候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is now occurring on a far greater scale
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.56,0:36:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,已经造成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a consequence
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.76,0:36:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,更大规模的人类与野生动物的冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the way we are changing the world's climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.52,0:36:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一些干旱地区\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some arid regions
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.00,0:36:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如今正经历着异常的强降水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are now experiencing unusually high rainfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.40,0:36:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这对于在非洲东北部的庄稼种植\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that is good for growing crops
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.92,0:36:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是个好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}here in northeastern Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.44,0:36:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然而 这样的气候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's also the perfect conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.40,0:36:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也大大滋生了一种昆虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for one particular insect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.08,0:37:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠蝗虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Desert locusts.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.92,0:37:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沙漠蝗虫一般是独居动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're normally solitary creatures,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.32,0:37:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但种群数量的大幅增长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but emerging from the sand in great numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.20,0:37:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,引发了沙漠蝗虫的剧变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}triggers a dramatic physical change.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,它们变成了鲜艳的黄色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They turn a vivid yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.72,0:37:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,并且高度社会化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and become highly social.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.40,0:37:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,成为了一支无可阻挡的军队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together, they are an unstoppable army.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.88,0:37:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,依靠步行 它们一天可以翻越近两公里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}On foot, they can cover a mile a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.32,0:38:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,但步行只能到此为止\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they can only go so far in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.40,0:38:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,它们需要爬到高处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need to find height.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.36,0:38:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里 蝗虫开始了最后的转变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up here, they begin their final transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.44,0:38:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,通常 一只昆虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Normally, it takes an individual insect
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.08,0:38:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,至少需要一个月才能羽化成虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}at least a month to become a winged adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.88,0:38:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这支蝗虫军队里 发育速度大幅提高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but in their social form, their development speeds up.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.48,0:39:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,万事俱备 只等翅膀硬化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now all they need is for their wings to harden.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.24,0:39:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,蝗群一天可以飞越100公里的距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once airborne, they can travel 60 miles in a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.56,0:39:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,蝗群合并在一起 变成了一场灾难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swarms merge and they become a plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.72,0:39:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这群数以十亿计的蝗群\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one contains billions of individuals,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.28,0:39:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一天内啃食的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and eats as much in a day
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.48,0:39:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,与整个德国相当\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the entire population of Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.12,0:40:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 在非洲东北部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today in northeastern Africa,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.20,0:40:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,由于气候变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a consequence of climate change...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.64,0:40:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭性的蝗灾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...devastating surges of locusts
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.20,0:40:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越频繁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are becoming more frequent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.12,0:40:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,人类世界与自然世界正在碰撞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two worlds are colliding.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.52,0:41:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,无意中 人类恰好创造了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unintentionally, humanity has created exactly the conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.56,0:41:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,导致这种物种数量激增的条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that cause this species to explode in numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.44,0:41:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,而同时还有另一群动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But another group of animals has seen
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.20,0:41:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们的行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an even more dramatic rise
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.68,0:41:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,数量发生了更为急剧的增长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as a consequence of OUR actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.44,0:41:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几乎将一些物种的数量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have increased the numbers of a few species
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.64,0:41:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,提高到了天文数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}almost astronomically.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.44,0:41:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,按重量计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.88,0:41:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如今世界上70%的鸟类都是家鸡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}70% of the world's birds are now chickens
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.92,0:42:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,以及其他家禽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or other domesticated fowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.20,0:42:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每年饲养700亿只家畜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We rear 70 billion farm animals each year...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.68,0:42:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,需要大量的饲料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and every one of them needs feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.80,0:42:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为这么多家畜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Producing the food
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.76,0:42:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,生产提供饲料\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for such numbers of domesticated animals
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.00,0:42:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对自然界造成了深远的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is having a profound impact on the natural world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.84,0:42:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,亚马逊雨林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Amazon rainforest -
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.40,0:42:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,面积是印度的两倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}twice the size of India.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.56,0:42:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的物种是如此丰富\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's so rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.08,0:42:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,地球上十分之一的物种都生活在此处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it contains one in every ten species on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.88,0:43:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是这只树懒以及它十个月大的孩子的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's home to this sloth and her ten-month-old baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.76,0:43:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,小树懒出生在一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was born into an environment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.44,0:43:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎未受人类破坏的环境中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}virtually untouched by humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.20,0:43:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但如今人类正在染指这片净土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But now human beings are claiming even this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.28,0:44:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,年复一年 人类开垦亚马逊雨林的面积\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Year after year, we clear over two million hectares
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.40,0:44:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,已超过两百万公顷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of the Amazon forest -
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.24,0:44:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,相当于整个威尔士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}an area the size of Wales.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.52,0:44:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将每一寸土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we use nearly all of it
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.92,0:44:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,都用作牛群的养殖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make more space for cattle...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.68,0:44:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以及大豆的种植 以喂养家畜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and to grow soya to feed our livestock.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.28,0:44:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 我们给世界各地的野生动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today, habitat destruction is the biggest problem
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.44,0:44:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,造成的最大问题 便是栖息地破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have created for wildlife around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.12,0:44:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这只豪猪在火灾中幸存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This porcupine has survived the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.64,0:44:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,被救了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and is being rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.44,0:45:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,豪猪被重新送到原始森林中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's being relocated to pristine forests.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.64,0:45:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这将是它新的家园\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will be its new home.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.28,0:45:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然而只有少数幸运的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only a fortunate few animals
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.52,0:45:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了继续生存的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are being given such a second chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.60,0:45:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,健康的自然世界 不仅对野生动物至关重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A healthy natural world is not only vital for wildlife...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.00,0:45:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也是人类生存的关键\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but for our own very existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.80,0:46:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须设法恢复生态平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Somehow we must find ways to redress the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.92,0:46:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,目前 绝大多数农业用地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Currently, the vast majority of agricultural land,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.44,0:46:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,超过75%\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more than 75%,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.68,0:46:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被用来饲养家畜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is used to raise livestock,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.36,0:46:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而这十分低效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and this is very inefficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.80,0:46:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有一些解决方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.56,0:46:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,其中一种是改变饮食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One is considering what we eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.92,0:46:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们从肉奶制品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we shift away from eating meat and dairy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.20,0:46:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,转向植食性饮食\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and move towards a plant-based diet,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.40,0:46:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,太阳能就可以直接用来种植我们需要的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then the sun's energy goes directly into growing our food.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.44,0:47:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,而且因为这样效率更高\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And because that's so much more efficient,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要四分之一的土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we could still produce enough to feed us,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.52,0:47:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就能养活全人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but do so using a quarter of the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.32,0:47:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以腾出相当于\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This could free up an area the size of the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.88,0:47:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,美国 中国 欧盟国家以及澳大利亚总和的面积\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}China, the European Union and Australia combined...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.88,0:47:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这些土地将得以回归自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...space that could then be given back to nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.32,0:47:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的创新也许能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And human innovations may be able
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.96,0:47:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,为野生动物做到更多的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to do even more for wildlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.68,0:47:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 高科技农场可以垂直种植\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}High-tech farms now grow plants vertically,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.20,0:47:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,产量是同等土地的350倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}yielding up to 350 times the food grown in the same area.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.68,0:48:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是众多解决方案之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is one of many solutions we already have,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.08,0:48:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且肯定还有更多解决方案等待我们探索\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and others are surely on the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.92,0:48:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找保护地球一切生命的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To find ways to protect all life on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.20,0:48:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,意味着去重新想象我们未来的生活方式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}means reimagining how we live on this planet in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.32,0:48:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的创造力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Human ingenuity,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.16,0:48:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,寻求解决方案的非凡能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}our extraordinary ability to find solutions,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.60,0:48:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,让未来充满了希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gives me hope that we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.96,0:48:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是这一代人与下一代人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will be the major challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.28,0:48:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,将要面临的主要挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for this generation and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.28,0:49:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}幕后花絮
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.08,0:49:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拍摄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To film the impact
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.80,0:49:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾对亚马逊雨林的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that fires are having on the Amazon,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.92,0:49:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,「地球脉动 III」摄制组\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Planet Earth III team
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.28,0:49:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,加入了一个当地的志愿消防队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}joined a local volunteer fire brigade.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.00,0:49:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,消防队正在应对一片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fire brigade are responding to a patch
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.24,0:49:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,正在燃烧的原始雨林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of primary rainforest that is burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.76,0:49:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾已经持续两天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's been burning for two days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.48,0:49:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很难说我们会看到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's difficult to know what we're going to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.88,0:49:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾主因是人为非法放火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fires are mainly lit illegally...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.44,0:49:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,从而给牛群腾出空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...to clear space for cattle.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.44,0:49:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,情况很严峻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's really intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.44,0:49:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这大火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look at the fires over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.44,0:49:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没见过这么大规模的火灾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never seen anything like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.44,0:49:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快用水泵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on use the water pump!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.44,0:49:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,离远一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do it from far!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.44,0:49:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把角落处的火扑灭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop that fire on the corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.56,0:50:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,灭火工作十分危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Battling fires is dangerous work.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.64,0:50:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但消防员每天都要面对这种危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the firefighters face them every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.24,0:50:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,对于摄制组来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For the wildlife film crew,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.28,0:50:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个全新的体验\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is a totally new experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.24,0:50:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾形势难以预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And these fires can be unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.16,0:50:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,尼尔 别在里面逗留太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neil, don't spend long in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.16,0:50:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得小心 防止火情蔓延到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to be careful so the fire doesn't get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.16,0:50:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的风向有些危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The way the wind is right now it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.16,0:50:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得撤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we've got to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.16,0:50:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,延时摄像机交给我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll get the timelapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.12,0:50:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.12,0:50:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,往这儿跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Run this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.12,0:50:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太吓人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's quite scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.60,0:50:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,随着地面团队的后撤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With the ground team retreating,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.40,0:50:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,最安全的拍摄方式是用无人机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the safest way to carry on filming is with the drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.32,0:51:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,-无人机没了吗 -我想阿比看见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have we lost the drone? I think Abi has seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.36,0:51:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阿比在路上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Abi is on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.56,0:51:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你能确认你在去往无人机的路上吗 阿比\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you confirm you're on your way to the drone, Abi?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.04,0:51:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机飞进火焰里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The drone has gone up in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.04,0:51:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我找到无人机了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have the drone.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.04,0:51:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,坠毁在我们面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It crashed in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.04,0:51:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,烧毁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.04,0:51:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无人机彻底报废了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The drone is damaged beyond repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.72,0:51:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.36,0:52:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about it. It's absolutely fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-怎么会没关系 -真的没关系的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not OK. It is. It's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.60,0:52:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有备用设备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's equipment. We've got a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.32,0:52:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是 每个人都安然无恙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The main thing is, we're all safe. No-one's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.64,0:52:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制组重整旗鼓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The team regroup...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.52,0:52:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,决定离开火灾的中心地带\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and decide to move away from the heart of the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.96,0:52:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,前往边缘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to its fringes
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.08,0:52:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找被火焰困住的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to look for animals caught up in the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.40,0:52:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,报告说树上有只猴子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's been reports of a monkey in the trees, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.00,0:52:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.28,0:52:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是 一路上都是火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The problem is, there's fires all the way along here,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.52,0:52:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也一路上都是火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as well as all along here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.92,0:52:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很难知道这些野生动物在家园烧毁时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's hard to know what all this wildlife is going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.08,0:52:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,会作何反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when their home is burnt up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.32,0:52:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道对于这些雨林野生动物来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what it's like for these rainforest animals
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.36,0:52:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,经历火灾是什么感受\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to be experiencing a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.84,0:52:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说太可怕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's horrific for me, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.84,0:52:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道对它们来说怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I don't know what it is for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.00,0:53:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,火灾彻夜燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fires burn into the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.08,0:53:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,第二天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The following day,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.12,0:53:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,摄制组陪同消防员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the crew accompany the firefighters
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.04,0:53:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在灾后废墟中寻找动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the search for animals in the aftermath.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.24,0:53:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 里面火还没熄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God, there are flames all inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.00,0:53:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,小白蚁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little termite...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.20,0:53:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.00,0:53:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,令人惊讶的是 有些动物得以幸存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remarkably, some animals have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.00,0:53:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,太令人难过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For me, it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.00,0:53:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然是有生命的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because nature is alive, just like we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.00,0:54:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和人类没什么两样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything that we have, it has too
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.00,0:54:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,看到森林被烧毁成这样真的很难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so it's sad to see the forest like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.00,0:54:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然应该被善待 而不应如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It deserves more, it shouldn't be treated like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.00,0:54:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,强盛的大自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It must be strong
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.00,0:54:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能给予我们力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to give us strength
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.00,0:54:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,大自然满目疮痍 人类也只会变得更孱弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because if it gets weaker, we will feel weaker
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.00,0:54:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,一荣俱荣一损俱损\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and if it falls, we all fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.40,0:54:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,农业用地的开垦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Clearing land for farming
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.24,0:54:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是亚马逊雨林独有的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is not a problem unique to the Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.80,0:54:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,农业土地占据了地球上一半的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Agriculture now takes up half of the habitable land
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.64,0:54:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,栖息地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.36,0:54:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,生产食物的同时减少对自然世界的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To produce food with less impact on the natural world
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.32,0:54:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,需要新方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}requires new approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.40,0:54:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,因此摄制组来到了一个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that led the wildlife film crew to a farm
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.36,0:55:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,仓库里的农场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in a warehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.04,0:55:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们身在城市中心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in the middle of the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.88,0:55:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,难以置信 这么小的空间里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't believe so much food
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.08,0:55:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,能种出这么多食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}being grown in such a small space!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.40,0:55:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在距亚马逊雨林一万公里外的洛杉矶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here in Los Angeles, 6,000 miles from the Amazon,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.88,0:55:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这个农场是蓬勃发展的食物革命的一部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this farm is part of a burgeoning food revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.00,0:55:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界上最高产的农场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the most productive farm in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.32,0:55:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的目标是将种植食物所需的土地和资源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it's our goal to reduce the amount of land and resources
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.08,0:55:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,减少到最低限度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}necessary to grow down to the bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.48,0:55:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,明白这一点需要时间 对于自然来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It took a while to understand that, for nature,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.92,0:55:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,开垦农业用地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}agricultural use of land
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.96,0:55:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类最主要的破坏性活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}was the primary, like, destructive behaviour of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.64,0:55:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,随着这种种植方式的扩张\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As we expand this means of growing,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.84,0:55:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最终可以将很多土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm very hopeful that this approach can ultimately
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.00,0:55:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,归还大自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}give a lot of land back to nature
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.24,0:55:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,使生物多样性得以重新繁荣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and allow that biodiversity to re-establish and flourish.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.36,0:55:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个农场不仅占地面积小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not only does this farm use less space...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.04,0:56:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,而且节约了90%的水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...but it also uses 90% less water,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.24,0:56:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不使用农药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no pesticides,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.64,0:56:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,减少食物运输距离\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and cuts food miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.68,0:56:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个很好的开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It does feel like a really good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.64,0:56:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的创意可以减少我们对地球的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ideas like this can reduce our footprint on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.84,0:56:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给自然世界一个恢复的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}giving the natural world a chance to bounce back.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.92,0:56:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下一集\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Next time,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.68,0:56:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在一线拯救野生动物的英雄们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the heroes on the frontline saving wildlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.28,0:56:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,探索偏远的丛林\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're exploring remote jungles...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.88,0:56:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密抓捕罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...working undercover to catch criminals...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.72,0:56:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,保证濒危物种的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and leading endangered creatures to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.08,0:57:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,「栖息地探索者」生动地展现动物和它们的栖息地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Habitat Explorer brings animals and their habitats to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.28,0:57:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,探索这个免费互动程序并制作折纸动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Explore this free interactive and make origami animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.92,0:57:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,前往bbc.co.uk/planetearth3\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.00,0:57:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,点击链接进入开放大学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and follow the links to the Open University.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.24,0:57:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,或者订购免费印刷版\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or to order a free printed version, visit the website
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.64,0:57:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎访问网站或拨打屏幕上的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or call the number on the screen.

